---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Matej Vavro Productivity">
	<div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 max-w-4xl">
		<header class="text-center mb-12 reveal">
			<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-(--color-text-purple) mb-4">Matej Vavro Productivity</h1>
			<p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-(--color-text-muted) font-light">
				Everything can be further improved — and then some more.
			</p>
		</header>

		<main class="space-y-8">
			<div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
				<p class="text-lg text-(--color-text) leading-relaxed reveal">
					Software Tools, Second Brains, and Personal Knowledge Management systems used for productivity and organization.
				</p>

				<p class="text-lg text-(--color-text) leading-relaxed mt-6 reveal">
					In particular, tools that allow you to create clarity and structure. As a developer, I constantly refine my own systems to make them more flexible and effective. I cover workflows and strategies that prioritize automation and efficiency with the ultimate end goal of helping you achieve focus, work towards your goals, and achieve meaningful results in times where clarity is everything.
				</p>

				<p class="text-lg text-(--color-text) leading-relaxed mt-6 reveal">
					When existing solutions feel inefficient, I build my own. This channel documents that entire process — identifying gaps and designing better systems.
				</p>

				<p class="text-lg text-(--color-text) leading-relaxed mt-6 reveal">
					If you want to get somewhere in life, let's cooperate. Through trial and error, we iterate, continuously improve, and build something superior that can stand the test of time in an age of both distraction and incredible opportunity. This is the great filter that separates the successful from the lost.
				</p>

				<p class="text-lg text-(--color-text) leading-relaxed mt-6 font-semibold reveal">
					Welcome aboard.
				</p>

				<p class="text-lg text-(--color-text) leading-relaxed mt-6 font-semibold reveal">
					CAA
				</p>
			</div>

	<div class="text-center my-8 reveal">
		<a
			href="https://www.youtube.com/@MatejVavroProductivity?sub_confirmation=1"
			target="_blank"
			rel="noopener noreferrer"
			class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-(--color-secondary) hover:text-(--color-secondary-light) font-semibold text-lg transition-all duration-200 hover:scale-105"
		>
			<svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
				<path d="M23.498 6.186a3.016 3.016 0 0 0-2.122-2.136C19.505 3.545 12 3.545 12 3.545s-7.505 0-9.377.505A3.017 3.017 0 0 0 .502 6.186C0 8.07 0 12 0 12s0 3.93.502 5.814a3.016 3.016 0 0 0 2.122 2.136c1.871.505 9.376.505 9.376.505s7.505 0 9.377-.505a3.015 3.015 0 0 0 2.122-2.136C24 15.93 24 12 24 12s0-3.93-.502-5.814zM9.545 15.568V8.432L15.818 12l-6.273 3.568z"/>
			</svg>
			Watch on YouTube
		</a>
	</div>

	<div class="flex justify-center my-8 reveal">
		<script async data-uid="287dc53339" src="https://matej-vavro-productivity.kit.com/287dc53339/index.js"></script>
	</div>

			<div class="text-center mt-12 reveal">
				<a
					href="/start"
					class="inline-block px-8 py-4 bg-(--color-primary) text-white font-semibold rounded-lg transition-colors text-lg btn-lift"
				>
					Start here
				</a>
			</div>
		</main>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>
